## 3. Reader

Purpose

Read without distractions.

Contains:

Book
Reader toolbar
Reader settings
Page preview
Dictionary
Highlights

This is where users spend 90% of their time.

## 4. Highlights & Notes

Purpose:

Everything you've highlighted.

Contains:

Highlights
Notes
Quotes
Export

Question for you:

Do we make this a separate scene?

Or place it inside Library?

I'm leaning toward separate, because some readers use highlights heavily.

